&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities include&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the strategy and growth plan for a portfolio of Priority Accounts, with a focus on retention, expansion, and long-term value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead account planning by defining client goals, identifying opportunities, and building clear, actionable plans to drive revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Sales to prioritize opportunities, align on strategy, and ensure a clear path to achieving client goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Sight and Strategy to translate first-party search and zero-party data into insights, narratives, and recommendations across the sales cycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the market intelligence narrative in QBRs and ongoing client conversations, bringing forward trends, insights, and clear strategic recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain senior-level relationships across client and agency teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to expand across channels, products, and data solutions within VFA&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive alignment across internal teams to ensure work is prioritized and focused on the highest-impact opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify gaps, risks, and opportunities within accounts and take action to address them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
